{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/awesome-tool-boop/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"p3t.lu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"61eda477-6bec-5a41-9bdd-eab4dbfb2980","excerpt":"睡前在推特上閒晃看到 Boop 這個小工具，馬上把自己能分享的管道全部傳一輪，容我簡短的罵個髒話，幹幹幹幹幹幹，這真的是太讚了！！！平常工作與生活中就很常有這種需求，把字串轉來轉去，解開來又編回去之類的，我個人是蠻在意把一些有機敏資訊的字串貼到隨便 google 來的網頁上做轉換，所以也找了幾個能在 CLI…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; border-style: solid; border-width: thin; border-color: #334747;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/c2d9c/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.37974683544303%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"awesome tool boop ui\"\n        title=\"awesome tool boop ui\"\n        src=\"/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/f058b/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/c26ae/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 158w,\n/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/6bdcf/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 315w,\n/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/f058b/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 630w,\n/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/40601/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 945w,\n/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/78612/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 1260w,\n/static/c1313ac8fa835278bdaeef37c4baa21a/c2d9c/awesome-tool-boop-ui.png 1326w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>睡前在推特上閒晃看到 <a href=\"https://boop.okat.best/\">Boop</a> 這個小工具，馬上把自己能分享的管道全部傳一輪，容我簡短的罵個髒話，幹幹幹幹幹幹，這真的是太讚了！！！平常工作與生活中就很常有這種需求，把字串轉來轉去，解開來又編回去之類的，我個人是蠻在意把一些有機敏資訊的字串貼到隨便 google 來的網頁上做轉換，所以也找了幾個能在 CLI 的解決方法，是說這些字串留在 shell history 中我也是覺得很母湯，打完我還會手動去把 history 清乾淨，這個 Boop 的出現真的是完完全全打中我的點啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！Boop 太好用了，有哪些功能就請各位自行去玩玩看啦！看它熱門的程度未來會支援的功能絕對會更加豐富，以下就來介紹一下平常在 CLI 會用到的解決方案 XD (試想一下未來有一天你沒 Boop 的時候該怎麼辦？)</p>\n<h2>Base64</h2>\n<p>encode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ echo 'base64' | base64\nYmFzZTY0Cg==</code></pre></div>\n<p>decode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ echo 'YmFzZTY0Cg==' | base64 --decode\nbase64</code></pre></div>\n<h2>URL</h2>\n<p>encode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ python3 -c \"import sys, urllib.parse as ul;print(ul.quote_plus(sys.argv[1]))\" 'param1=god&amp;param2=dog'\nparam1%3Dgod%26param2%3Ddog</code></pre></div>\n<p>decode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ python3 -c \"import sys, urllib.parse as ul;print(ul.unquote_plus(sys.argv[1]))\" 'param1%3Dgod%26param2%3Ddog'\nparam1=god&amp;param2=dog</code></pre></div>\n<h2>HTML</h2>\n<p>encode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ python3 -c \"import sys, html;print(html.escape(sys.argv[1]))\" 'A>B&amp;C'\nA&amp;gt;B&amp;amp;C</code></pre></div>\n<p>decode</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ python3 -c \"import sys, html;print(html.unescape(sys.argv[1]))\" 'A&amp;gt;B&amp;amp;C'\nA>B&amp;C</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Format JSON</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ echo '{\"key1\":\"value1\",\"key2\":123,\"key3\":[\"v\",\"a\",\"l\",\"u\",\"e\",\"3\"]}' | jq\n{\n  \"key1\": \"value1\",\n  \"key2\": 123,\n  \"key3\": [\n    \"v\",\n    \"a\",\n    \"l\",\n    \"u\",\n    \"e\",\n    \"3\"\n  ]\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Count Characters</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ echo '0123456789\n  9876543210' | wc -c\n      22</code></pre></div>\n<h2>MD5 Checksum</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">⟩ echo 'test' | md5sum\nd8e8fca2dc0f896fd7cb4cb0031ba249  -</code></pre></div>\n<h2>總結</h2>\n<p>以上就是幾個日常比較常用到的方法，有些用到 Python 其實有點作弊，不過 alias 起來也是可以用的嚇嚇叫的！然後 Boop 真的很讚，能用快點用，用好用滿！</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"發現超好用小工具 Boop！如果沒有它，在 CLI 要如何解決？","date":"June 16, 2020","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lets-meet-bot/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"幫忙找出中心座標的 Telegram bot"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fish-shell-slow-issue/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"解決我的 fish shell 變慢的問題"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"61eda477-6bec-5a41-9bdd-eab4dbfb2980","previousPostId":"b256beef-a3aa-5095-98a4-884aabefa75f","nextPostId":"569b5ba1-e0a6-559e-b058-18a4738f2bb4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3624854548","548598555"]}